91% said that they have an unmanageable amount of stress. When they do, it negatively impacts

124
00:06:40,172 --> 00:06:45,876
the quality of their work. 83% said burnout from work negatively impacts their personal

125
00:06:45,916 --> 00:06:47,558
relationships. And here's the important point.

126
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:52,722
87% say they're passionate about their current job,

127
00:06:53,242 --> 00:06:55,984
but 64% say they're still frequently stressed.

128
00:06:56,525 --> 00:07:01,508
Passion does not exclude or make impossible getting burned out

129
00:07:01,588 --> 00:07:02,389
and getting stressed.

