00:20:09,280 --> 00:20:11,562
that he would use in his opening when he gets distracted.

382
00:20:13,883 --> 00:20:16,865
May he who illuminated this illuminate me.

383
00:20:18,246 --> 00:20:20,748
And that's a good example of the kind of thing

384
00:20:21,368 --> 00:20:23,910
that you would use as a focus during your opening.

385
00:20:25,231 --> 00:20:26,191
A couple other examples.

