00:23:36,730 --> 00:23:41,554
I am seeing and experiencing this different world.

442
00:23:42,075 --> 00:23:44,937
And now I have to come back and relay it

443
00:23:44,957 --> 00:23:48,039
to people playing the game in a way that makes them

